            <title>[LUCENE-1082] IndexReader.lastModified - throws NPE</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LUCENE-1082</link>
                <project id="12310110" key="LUCENE">Lucene - Core</project>
                        <description>&lt;p&gt;IndexReader.lastModified(String dir) or its variants always return NPE on 2.3, perhaps something to do with SegmentInfo.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>&lt;p&gt;Windows variants.&lt;/p&gt;</environment>
